Review comment:
       Would it make sense to have `arrow_vendored::date::choose` as a template parameter rather than passing options every time the kernel is called? (I'm not certain just asking)
   
   Also note that we could probably do more templating for the [ceil/floor/round kernels](https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ARROW-15787), but that's out of scope here.

